        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "After serializing and unserializing a Zend_Pdf object with pages everything seems ok until you add additional pages to the object.\r\nRendered PDF is corrupt, it contains unreadable text (font information missing?), blank pages appear and pages are repeated randomly.\r\n\r\nsniplet to reproduce behauviour:\r\n{code}\r\nif (!isset($_SESSION['PDF'])) {\r\n\r\n    $pdf = new Zend_Pdf();\r\n\r\n    $pdf->pages[] = $objPage = new Zend_Pdf_Page(Zend_Pdf_Page::SIZE_A4);\r\n    $objPage->setFont(Zend_Pdf_Font::fontWithName(Zend_Pdf_Font::FONT_HELVETICA), 16);\r\n    $objPage->drawText('Page ' . count($pdf->pages), 100, 150);\r\n\r\n    $pdf->pages[] = $objPage = new Zend_Pdf_Page(Zend_Pdf_Page::SIZE_A4);\r\n    $objPage->setFont(Zend_Pdf_Font::fontWithName(Zend_Pdf_Font::FONT_HELVETICA), 16);\r\n    $objPage->drawText('Page ' . count($pdf->pages), 100, 150);\r\n\r\n    $_SESSION['PDF'] = serialize($pdf);\r\n    echo 'object serialized';\r\n} else {\r\n\r\n    $pdf = unserialize($_SESSION['PDF']);\r\n\r\n    $pdf->pages[] = $objPage = new Zend_Pdf_Page(Zend_Pdf_Page::SIZE_A4);\r\n    $objPage->setFont(Zend_Pdf_Font::fontWithName(Zend_Pdf_Font::FONT_HELVETICA), 16);\r\n    $objPage->drawText('Page ' . count($pdf->pages), 100, 150);\r\n\r\n    $pdf->pages[] = $objPage = new Zend_Pdf_Page(Zend_Pdf_Page::SIZE_A4);\r\n    $objPage->setFont(Zend_Pdf_Font::fontWithName(Zend_Pdf_Font::FONT_HELVETICA), 16);\r\n    $objPage->drawText('Page ' . count($pdf->pages), 100, 150);\r\n\r\n    header('Content-type: application\/pdf');\r\n    echo $pdf->render();\r\n\r\n    unset($_SESSION['PDF']);\r\n}\r\n{code}"
        },
